name: Vendetta WebBrowser
body:
### Vendeta WebBrowser.
Simple Open-source iOS webBrowser, has simple functions such as:

```
Themes
Bookmarks
History
and others...
```
Feel free to contribute to the project
### @pod32g
This project was started and is maintained by (@pod32g).
